CHANGELOG

2014-11-21  Kevin Chan  <kefin@makedostudio.com>

        * Bumped version to 0.1.10.
        * Added garage.tests.imports -- test various functions, classes
        and vars to ensure they are importable/exist.
        * Corrected misplacement of warning message under import django
        settings.
        * Corrected mistake in module_exists function; added
        function_exists and var_exists (garage.test.utils).
        * Bumped version to 0.1.9.
        * Added/updated from __future__ import statements (import
        absolute_import, unicode_literals).
        * Change import text_utils to import garage.text_utils (use
        abosolute import) (utils).

2014-08-23  Kevin Chan  <kefin@makedostudio.com>

        * Bumped version to 0.1.8.
        * Bumped version to 0.1.7.
        * Updated image_utils to import from Pillow (instead of obsolete
        PIL).
        * Claned up sources (moved import statements into functions to
        avoid potential import glitches).

2013-04-16  Kevin Chan  <kefin@makedostudio.com>

        * Added utility functions (garage.datetime) to convert datetime
        objects between timezones.
        * Bumped version to 0.1.6.

2013-01-12  Kevin Chan  <kefin@makedostudio.com>

        * packaged garage repository into preliminary app distribution.
